The paper deals with ad allocation problems, which are related to game theory (cs.GT) and data structures (cs.DS). The algorithms and analysis involve optimization techniques (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.MA) for targeted advertising. The paper also discusses the use of randomized algorithms (cs.AI) and their performance in comparison to deterministic algorithms.
